      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.MDgUy3mrWNR7l77y]{Seer Anchor}</p>\n<p>Once per day when you regain your spells, you can perform a divination for each of your allies, giving them a glimpse into their future and a better understanding of their past. If you do so, you can bestow a free paradox to all allies within 30 feet of you, up to a maximum number equal to your Dexterity modifier. They can use their paradox in place of their d20 roll for any one of the following: Perception checks, Sense Motive checks, skill checks made to recall knowledge. They canâ€™t use this paradox in any other way, and it expires after one day. Their paradox follows all the same rules as your paradoxes.</p>"
